Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:23.62,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Missing Link
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:02.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Missing Link."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:09.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It refers to that which is hidden behind a series\Nof incidents or seemingly unrelated victims:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:12.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Their common factor or underlying relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we are unable to seek out that link,\Nit remains difficult to solve cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, we will be presenting you a playback of a case\Ninvolving consecutive attacks on young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Causing your eyelids to swell and permeating your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tear drops serve as a prelude to a wealth of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sting operation has reopened the\Npast wounds of Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cell phone's battery ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got out of the carâ€”I'm in a phone booth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be at your place in about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:07.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,MEGURE'S SEALED SECRET\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, how's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a present for Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little cute for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This simple one will suit him just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No it won't, it's not hand-knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I just thought a hand-knit\Nsweater would feel warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I unintentionally mentioned it in\Nthe letter I sent him earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Right now, I'm knitting a sweater for someone I like."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never expected it to be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were going to buy him a hand-knit\Nsweater from a store and say you knit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know how to knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I admire your bravery in admitting that you\Nlike him, so I'll keep your secret to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I still haven't told Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say so in the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm knitting for someone I like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush or Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nmight think there's someone else you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, that's the whole point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will definitely panic a\Nbit when that comes to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day, a package will arrive at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would think, "What is this, something\Nfrom Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as he anxiously starts\Nto open up the package...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Surprise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The sweater was actually for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my marvelous love-love plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come crying to me if he's not impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} won't express his feelings, so I don't\Nknow how he actually feels if I don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know he worries about me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still need the courage to ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Ran, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} feels about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've known him since we were little, so it'd\Nbe a lie to say I don't want to know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"But, but, but, but, but, but, but, but, but...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I want to ask, but I'm afraid to know the answer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's how I feel right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thinking something\Ndreamy like that, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go to the parking garage and wait with Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Dad to go ahead and wait in the pasta\Nhouse behind this department store, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems I've come across some idle\Ngirl-talk that I shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that one's too tasteless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do girls like to spend so much time\Nshopping and chatting on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this cold and she's wearing a mini-skirt that short?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a ballpoint pen over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it belonged to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this belongs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguised in order to investigate the cases of\Nthe women who were attacked this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we asked Detective\NSatou to dress that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the announcements said the\Nsuspect is about 150 cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A quick look at me will tell you I'm\Nnot the suspect you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that attitude you had as you\Napproached Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I say "very special"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt I was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is tough to investigate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since the only common link between the women\Nwas that they were all wearing fashionable clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the crime scenes are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we see the photos of those three women again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first to be attacked goes by\Nthe name Mizutani Ryouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One night two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While she was waiting in her car for the traffic\Nlight to change, another car rear-ended her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as she left the vehicle to complain,\Nshe was attacked with a metal bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next one to be attacked was Endou Hitomi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten nights ago, she was struck by a metal bat as\Nshe was coming out of a public restroom in a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we have the one from last\Nnight, Ishiguro Michiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, she was attacked after\Ncoming out of a phone booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said phone boothâ€”does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was where we subdued you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the lives of those\Nthree victims aren't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just share nothing in common other than\Nthe fashionable garb they were wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of them also said they\Nhadn't made any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing I noticed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One thing you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them are mixed-race â€”\hlike\Nthey grew up in a jungle or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, they aren't normal Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These three ganguro look amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one in the middle is gonguro, so she's even darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This style is called Yamanba, and it's really\Nfashionable among girls these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamanba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you don't know, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Yamanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know something that obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she was going to the restroom and\Nwanted me to meet her at this pasta house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if this was just a series of random\Nattacks, there's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To now, there haven't been any cases like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there was one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a string of female high school\Nstudents being run over by cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty disturbing cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it was before I became a police detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we should get back to investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go back to being a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, a decoy is no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start over and investigate whether or not the\Nthree victims had any connection to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, sorry about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't find the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The underground parking garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you have no sense of direction, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, about your\Nring, necklace, and bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't they look like those worn\Nby the women in the photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't buy them, they were complimentary gifts\Nfrom that department store we just went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're having this Millennium Sale,\Nand they check your receipt at the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For every 10,000 yen you spend, you\Nget to choose one of the accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although they aren't wearing the entire set, they\Neach have a piece that matches Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means these three...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are all customers of that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Ran!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a girl whose face is covered in blood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Aizawa Tae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until one year ago, she worked in this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been unemployed since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So our fourth case is a murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same suspect, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We never announced the common\Ncharacteristics of the victims to the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the parking garage of\Nthat same department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no denying the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, this was done by someone bearing\Na grudge against this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed to have been waiting\Nfor her in the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:11.22,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shirakawa Noriyuki (24)\NCook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:09.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,His father is the owner of this department store...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:13.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And he planned to introduce his girlfriend\Nat the restaurant where he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a waitress who works in the\Nsame restaurant that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:25.45,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Konno Yuri (24)\NWaitress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Her name is Konno Yuri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:26.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She said they've been friends since college,\Nand that she sometimes gives him advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father opposed his\Nengagement with the deceased Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anyone suspicious\Nwhen you found the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person I passed by was the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the guard standing by the entrance when I\Ncame down â€”\ha man who was about 40 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I left my post in order to head to the restroom, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:59.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Sadakane Yoshio (43)\NGuard
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit must have got to her while I wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is, if you aren't really the culprit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, you worked at a rival\Ndepartment store until half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:17.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Could you have arranged with your former employer to\Ncause a scandal here and send my customers his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:17.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shirakawa Haruyoshi (53)\NHaido Department Store Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at least now Noriyuki can get a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, how about finding\Na nice girl with a clean slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, what did he mean by "clean slate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably referring to the automobile accident she\Nwas involved in a year ago, in this parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She ran over a little boy, and after\Nthat accident, she gave up her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi from the traffic division told me about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:15:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy was waiting in this parking garage for his\Nmother when he stepped in front of a car and was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver was going at a slow speed considering\Nit was the inside of a parking garage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the boy's vitals were\Nhit, and he died three days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the boy's name was Sakurai Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Noriyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how tall your father is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little over 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,173 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm 144 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm 167 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things aren't looking good for the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would've known when she would be by her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was your father already at the\Nrestaurant when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't show up on time, so\NI asked her to see if he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be implying that my father is a suspect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we only asked because the other victims told\Nus the culprit's height was around 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "other victims"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as I thought, this is the work of that\Nserial attacker we've been hearing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you done about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even know the culprit's height,\Nso why can't you catch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had caught the culprit, Tae wouldn't be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Noriyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae is dead, and it's the fault of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You police are all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Noriyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You police are all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I was going to play decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess... it didn't go smoothly like in the movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just went a little overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, it might be best for\Nhim to go cool off for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll return to my post.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did all three of those ladies attest that\Nthe culprit's height was around 150 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only the first and third victims said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second victim was suddenly attacked from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was unconscious until a passerby found her,\Nso she didn't catch a glimpse of her assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, both that did say were certain\Nthat the culprit was about 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we called them down to the\Nstation a few days after the attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both stated that their attacker was\Nroughly the same height as they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how tall were those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first was 151 cm, and the third was 153 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We measured them at the station,\Nso there's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell a kid too much about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran around looking for the exit, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, don't you think something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that lady there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you noticed it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's weird, but I can't figure out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person... something just isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of weird, don't you think the\Nsecond victim's clothes are weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lady was attacked as she was\Nleaving a park restroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took that picture right after\Nwe arrived at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restroom is even in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since a passerby was the one who found\Nher, she must have been alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if so, why is it she has a\Nman's coat on her shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the coat I loaned her at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why was she wearing such light\Nclothes in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't say anything about the\Nattacker stealing her coat or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, we haven't had time to take her\Nstatement since she's still in a state of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know it's fashionable\Nfor girls not to wear much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what she wore was sleeveless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be too cold for anyone to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was somewhere warm and had planned\Nto go back there after going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her car?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, the first and third victims were\Nattacked right after they left their cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, the fourth happened in a parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These cases all involve cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go contact the second\Nvictim immediately to confirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the owner's no longer suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your continued perseverance, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.78,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Matsumoto Kiyonaga (54)\NPolice Headquarters Â· Superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The press has already started reporting that\Nthis is the beginning of a serial murder spree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I advise you pull back for now and start\Nthe investigation anew tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already know the girls were\Nin their cars before the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just disguise as a ganguro\Nand act as a decoy in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No more decoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, allow us to investigate just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we're getting somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have a feeling that the culprit\Nis still around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're still thinking\Nback to that case from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what it is you hide away under your hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:46.30,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,MEGURE'S SEALED SECRET\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow your keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case seems like it's gonna take a while, so I'd\Nlike to put my stuff in the car and visit the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The store will be closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you take mine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, look at how this other car is parked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a strange way to park!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even open the passenger side door like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I just heard back from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, she was in her car\Nbefore going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is he only after fashionable\Nyoung girls who drive cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there some other connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that we overlooked connecting those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.93,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,RESTROOM CLOSED\NFOR CLEANING
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.93,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Please accept our\Napologies for the\Ninconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.93,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Haido\NDEPARTMENT STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't they wait to clean until after they've closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next restroom is up on the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have such bad luck with these restrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:29.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for visiting our department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:31.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We'll be closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.99,0:24:33.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please come again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.33,0:24:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take the body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, her leg slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.50,0:24:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shoe doesn't fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:24:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.22,0:25:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said there was\Nsomething wrong with that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.40,0:25:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's part of the ganguro fashion,\Nthey shouldn't have been missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.28,0:25:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the culprit be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.00,0:25:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't turn the lights off!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.71,0:25:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.30,0:25:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.30,0:25:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Platform boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was killed in this\Nparking garage, was actually wearing platform boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeahâ€”it's part of the ganguro fashion, so\Nthey wouldn't wear low-heeled pumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.82,0:25:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.20,0:25:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.08,0:26:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would the criminal change the victim's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.21,0:26:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want anyone to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.21,0:26:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he only goes after women\Nwho drive with platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.42,0:26:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.17,0:26:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, the other three victims\Nfollowed the ganguro fashion as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.31,0:26:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, those three must\Nhave had platform boots too?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of platform boots...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The primary reason that Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ncaused that car accident a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was due to the fact she was\Ndriving with platform boots on...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.45,0:26:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which caused her braking to take longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.91,0:26:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard from Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.41,0:26:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased boy's mother and her ex-husband\Nargued that that was the cause of the accident, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.96,0:26:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The judge overruled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:26:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ex-husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.92,0:26:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.68,0:27:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They divorced after the husband became an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.76,0:27:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that man's name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.56,0:27:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sadakane, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.39,0:27:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, that was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.61,0:27:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.61,0:27:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the guard's name... Sadakane?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.78,0:27:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, then, could that mean the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.61,0:27:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.66,0:27:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi, go get information on\Nthat accident from a year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.62,0:27:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, go find the guard, Sadakane!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.29,0:27:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.92,0:27:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit only attacked women who drove\Nwhile wearing platform boots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.72,0:27:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From outside the car, the culprit can't see\Nwhat kind of shoes they're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.81,0:27:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we know that the victims\Nshop at this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.48,0:27:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, the only way the culprit would know\Nis to see them getting in and out of their cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.07,0:27:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it had to be the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.36,0:28:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the victims said the\Nculprit was about 150 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear the guard say he was 167 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.25,0:28:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just playing stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.83,0:28:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girls only said that the culprit\Nwas the same height as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.13,0:28:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At those times, they were wearing\Nplatform boots over 10 cm thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.93,0:28:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that really meant was that the\Nculprit must've been 10 cm taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.43,0:28:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.93,0:28:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We measured their heights at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they were coming for a police interview,\Nthey wouldn't wear informal platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.45,0:28:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if he wanted to kill Aizawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.87,0:28:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do it in this parking complex rather\Nthan just go straight to her house?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.04,0:28:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.50,0:28:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was 20 years old, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.08,0:28:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year ago when she caused the\Naccident, she was considered a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.21,0:29:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minors cannot have their addresses be\Nmade public according to the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.92,0:29:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, he waited at this department store\Nwhere his son died, hoping she'd return one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.60,0:29:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she didn't appear, he broke down and began\Nattacking any woman who drove in platform boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.70,0:29:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we got the backstory!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.83,0:29:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, the guard is the father of the\Nboy who died in the accident one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.83,0:29:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.79,0:29:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.92,0:29:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that... his car is still in the\Nparking garage, but he's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.01,0:29:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko hasn't come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.76,0:29:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she was just going to put her things\Nin the car and then going to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.77,0:29:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting her stuff in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.52,0:29:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the shoes Sonoko's wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.57,0:30:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.28,0:30:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.78,0:30:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.78,0:30:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until you hear what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.74,0:30:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.16,0:30:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right as I got out of the restroom,\Nthey turned the lights off...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.85,0:30:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.19,0:30:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.23,0:30:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.06,0:30:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just thought I heard something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.84,0:31:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She saw me... She saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.14,0:31:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She saw my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.72,0:31:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.48,0:31:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.77,0:31:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.40,0:31:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit saw Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} doing\Nsomething in the car with the keys in hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.57,0:31:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He mistook her for a driver with platform boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.19,0:31:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.07,0:31:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.07,0:31:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.08,0:31:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the line cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.99,0:31:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still connected, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.83,0:31:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only hear a machine's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.87,0:31:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A machine's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:46.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Please choose your background picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.38,0:31:49.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,Press the button when your pose is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a print club machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.68,0:31:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the department store, do they\Nhave a print club machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.14,0:31:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.81,0:32:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's two on the 10th floor, next\Nto the stairs for the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.06,0:32:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stores are closed, but\Nthe restaurants are still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was headed up there to use\Nthe elevator to make her way back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.78,0:32:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.61,0:32:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi, get the lights in the building back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure and Satou, take the elevator\Nand search from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.78,0:32:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The others, take the stairs and search bottom to top\Nin order to secure this girl and seize the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.37,0:32:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.96,0:32:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.79,0:32:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, the Inspector seems fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.96,0:32:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.26,0:32:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case has reminded him of the\Nfirst case he was involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.97,0:32:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your daughter\Nand the boy with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.06,0:33:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.39,0:33:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.64,0:33:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Sonoko's cell phone, no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the customers in the restaurants\Nhaven't seen them...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.73,0:33:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} must've run into the department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.49,0:33:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi, where're the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.74,0:33:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You girls are demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.16,0:33:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.25,0:33:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You disguise yourselves as cute girls in order to\Ncommit crimesâ€”you're nothing but little demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.59,0:33:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demons have no right to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.68,0:34:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.60,0:34:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.48,0:34:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.02,0:34:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.48,0:34:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.99,0:34:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a number of things\Nare falling simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.53,0:34:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.28,0:34:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.49,0:34:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.29,0:34:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be those little stones you put in a fish tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.87,0:34:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pet shop is on the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.58,0:34:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must mean she's on the 4th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.54,0:34:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Restaurant Floor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Books & Beauty, Photos, Denistry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Food, Housewares, CDs, Stationary
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Children's Apparel, Clocks, Glasses, Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Misses & Plus Size Women's Apparel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.90,0:34:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.69,0:34:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only intended to teach you a little lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.57,0:35:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you just had to go and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.70,0:35:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.67,0:35:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.08,0:35:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.29,0:35:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird, there's no one in the pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.51,0:35:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.30,0:35:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.47,0:35:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing's broken and there's nothing on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.47,0:35:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.47,0:35:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.97,0:35:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just had to see my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.32,0:35:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.29,0:35:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.37,0:35:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.67,0:36:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked if hurting others feels good to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.59,0:36:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may think you're punishing evil\Nand being a bringer of justice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.10,0:36:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just a high school girl who\Nwanted to put things in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.77,0:36:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did this not for the sake of seeking\Njustice nor for avenging your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.70,0:36:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it solely out of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.49,0:36:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you it was just a conceited, meaningless\Ndiversion that trifled with people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.08,0:36:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.18,0:36:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted that woman to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For her to wear proper shoes and\Napologize to my son in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.98,0:36:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.98,0:37:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That really was true in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.86,0:37:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.54,0:37:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.59,0:37:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.59,0:37:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.09,0:37:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.89,0:37:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, how did you know they were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.60,0:37:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.10,0:37:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was led here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.31,0:37:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By these Go stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.90,0:37:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.99,0:37:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just my old wound reopening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old wound from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.33,0:39:22.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Midoridai Police Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got that wound from a previous case?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.38,0:39:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.25,0:39:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure hides the scar by wearing that hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.47,0:39:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for a police officer, a scar is like a badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.47,0:39:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was more than twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.48,0:39:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it was back when Megure\Nwas still a rookie on the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.69,0:39:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.11,0:39:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case where someone was\Nrunning over high-school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.03,0:39:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.66,0:39:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit had been bullied by an all-girls gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.87,0:40:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was running them down in his car at\Nnight, when there was no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.84,0:40:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He targeted female delinquents\Nwho wore long, tight skirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.63,0:40:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ones they'd converted from their\Nschool uniforms to be their style.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.01,0:40:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, he only made light contact with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.68,0:40:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then it escalated and resulted in a fatality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.36,0:40:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We warned all students not to wear that style of\Nskirt, so the case was settled for a while, until...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.91,0:40:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A high school girl showed up\Nwanting to be used as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.62,0:40:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to find her friend's killer at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.54,0:40:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we tried to stop her, but it seemed\Nshe despised the police, so she insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.63,0:40:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With no other choice, I assigned\NMegure to keep an eye on her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.11,0:41:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit tried to run over and kill\Nboth Megure and the girl with his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.95,0:41:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, Megure remembered the car number, so the\Nsuspect was caught very quicklyâ€”but at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.12,0:41:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure only hit his head, but the girl's\Nentire body was gravely injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.63,0:41:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we arrived, she was covered\Nin blood, and barely breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.64,0:41:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the reason why the Inspector\Nhas always kept his hat on...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.93,0:41:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.64,0:41:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want others to ask him about the scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.44,0:41:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always been reminded of that horrible case.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.94,0:41:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Megure wears that\Nhatâ€”to seal away that scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.66,0:42:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scar that symbolizes that tragic memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.83,0:42:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why the Inspector was against using decoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.62,0:42:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want anyone else to die like that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.13,0:42:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.55,0:42:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only said that she was gravely injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.26,0:42:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.13,0:42:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, she's Megure'sâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.01,0:42:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Superintendent Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.01,0:42:26.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to have you come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.56,0:42:30.73,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Megure Midori\NMegure's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.14,0:42:30.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just left a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.11,0:42:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they came by as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.15,0:42:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they all took a breather from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.28,0:42:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scar on her forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.41,0:42:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.83,0:42:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.33,0:42:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you peel this apple for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.66,0:42:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, he enjoys being spoiled, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.13,0:42:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to toughen him up\Nso he can return to the force soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.84,0:42:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you would, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.18,0:43:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the Inspector said his wife,\NMidori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was a delinquent in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.52,0:43:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the real reason he wears that hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.52,0:43:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is because he doesn't want others to\Nmake fun of how he and his wife met?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.70,0:43:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heeey, not done yet?
